net.sf.mmm.client.ui.api.attribute

Interface AttributeReadRowSpan

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    AttributeWriteRowSpan
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractTableCellAtomic, AbstractTableCellComposite, TableCellAtomic, TableCellComposite, TableCellHeaderAtomic, TableCellHeaderComposite

    public interface AttributeReadRowSpan
    This interface gives read access to the rowSpan attribute of an object.
    Since:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Joerg Hohwiller (hohwille at users.sourceforge.net)

    • Field Detail

      • ATTRIBUTE_ROWSPAN

        static final String ATTRIBUTE_ROWSPAN
        The attribute name of getRowSpan().
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

    • Method Detail

      • getRowSpan

        int getRowSpan()
        This method gets the number of rows spanned by this object (cell). This cell expands to that number of cells vertically so a value greater than 1 indicates that the next cells to the bottom are connected.
        Returns:
        the row span. By default 1.
